🌐 Saran Babu Dannana — Personal Portfolio
A 3D animated personal portfolio website built with HTML, CSS, and Three.js.
Live at: sarandannana12.github.io

✨ Features
🎯 Interactive 3D animated background using Three.js
🌊 Smooth scroll fade-in animations on every section
📱 Fully responsive design for mobile and desktop
🔗 Clickable certificate and social links
⚡ Pure HTML/CSS/JS — no frameworks, no build tools

📂 Sections
Hero — Name, tagline, and call-to-action
About — Bio and contact details
Skills — Programming, Cloud, SAP, and tools
Experience — Internship timeline
Projects — Featured technical projects
Education — Academic background
Certifications — Verified credentials with links
Contact — Email, LinkedIn, GitHub
🛠️ Tech Stack
Technology	Usage
HTML5 / CSS3	Structure & styling
JavaScript (ES6)	Interactivity & animations
Three.js r128	3D background animation

🚀 Run Locally
No installation needed. Just clone and open:
git clone https://github.com/sarandannana12/sarandannana12.github.io.git
cd sarandannana12.github.io
# Open index.html in your browser

bash
git clone https://github.com/sarandannana12/sarandannana12.github.io.git
